                | anywhere, anytime a reality. But cloud is not one-size-fits-all. Organizations considering cloud
                | adoption must consider the right mix of on- and off-premises services that leverage the best of
                | traditional IT with private, managed and public cloud. Read on to learn more about how converged
                | infrastructure provides the ideal foundation for
                a(href='/Cloud')
                  b converged cloud
